{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_13","type":"agent_message","text":"I found the bad assumption: these PostgreSQL tests merge `stderr` into `stdout`, so a benign Docker warning corrupts the returned container ID. I’m checking whether there’s a shared helper I can fix once instead of patching each test ad hoc."}}
