ied with:\n`GRAALVM_HOME=/home/vjovanov/gdrive/bin/graalvm-jdk-25.0.3+9.1 GVM_TCK_NATIVE_IMAGE_MODE=current-defaults JAVA_HOME=/home/vjovanov/gdrive/bin/graalvm-jdk-25.0.3+9.1 ./gradlew testInfra -Pcoordinates=org.postgresql:postgresql:42.7.11 -Pparallelism=1 --stacktrace`\n\nThere are unrelated pre-existing modifications in other `stats/.../stats.json` files; I left those untouched."}}
